<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>진료 예약 방식 선택</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <!-- Header (PatientLayout) -->
    <header class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200 h-16 flex items-center px-8 justify-between shrink-0 sticky top-0 z-10">
        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2">
            <i data-lucide="stethoscope" class="text-indigo-600 w-6 h-6"></i>
            MediCare+
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">
            <i data-lucide="home" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
            처음으로
        </a>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">진료 예약</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500">원하시는 예약 방식을 선택해주세요.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 w-full max-w-4xl">
            <a href="/reservation/symptom-reservation" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all group flex flex-col items-center text-center cursor-pointer block">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <i data-lucide="activity" class="w-10 h-10"></i>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">AI 증상 추천 예약</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                    어디가 아픈지 증상을 입력하시면<br/>
                    AI가 적합한 진료과와 전문의를 추천해 드립니다.
                </p>
            </a>

            <a href="/reservation/direct-reservation" class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all group flex flex-col items-center text-center cursor-pointer block">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-10 h-10"></i>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">직접 선택 예약</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                    원하시는 진료과와 전문의,<br/>
                    예약 시간을 직접 선택하여 예약합니다.
                </p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        // 아이콘 초기화
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
